<h2>Education Opportunities</h2>
<h3>Practicum in Psychology</h3>
<p>Psychological Services of Pendleton, LLC provides educational opportunities for graduate students in clinical psychology. Supervised experience in assessment and psychotherapy is available to students interested in practicing in a rural setting. Applicants should be currently enrolled in a graduate program in clinical psychology.</p>
<p>Email Dr. Templeman at <a href="mailto:opportunities@pendletonpsych.com?subject=Education%20Opportunities%20at%20PSP">opportunities@pendletonpsych.com</a> for more information.</p>

<h3>Residency in Psychology</h3>
<p>Psychological Services of Pendleton, LLC offers a psychologist residency to meet requirements for licensure in Oregon. Supervised experience in assessment and psychotherapy is provided by licensed psychologists. Applicants must have doctorates in psychology from psychology programs approved by the Oregon Board of Psychologist Examiners.</p>
<p>Email Dr. Templeman at <a href="mailto:opportunities@pendletonpsych.com?subject=Education%20Opportunities%20at%20PSP">opportunities@pendletonpsych.com</a> for information about terms and earnings.</p>
